{"type": "article", "id": 21653, "title": "冬天里的白色和粉色，挑人但是真好看呐", "description": "冬天里最适合做长款大衣的颜色应该就是淡粉色了吧，一点都不娘，真的。", "date": "2016-02-02T10:00:23Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 22961, "name": "粉色"}, {"id": 10240, "name": "白色"}, {"id": 15331, "name": "简洁"}, {"id": 19175, "name": "冬天"}, {"id": 2711, "name": "穿搭"}, {"id": 15755, "name": "走秀"}, {"id": 16355, "name": "Acne"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 139, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061613204Mekzx3tSdEhv5uZ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">一到冬天，似乎满大街就很容易遍布“一身黑”的打扮，可能出于显瘦、耐脏、百搭等等各种各样的原因。这个时候人们还喜欢卡其色的羊绒大衣、军绿色的羽绒大衣……当然这些经典毋庸置疑，只是难免有些乏味、压抑。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">这时候白色和粉色就变得特别能让人眼前一亮。</p>\n<p class=\"\">就拿粉色来说吧，能穿的绝对不是多年前留在你深深脑海中的“阿 X 莲”那一种。这个色系还是很强大的，可以粉嫩温暖，也可以偏向骚气的玫红，或者稍微有点发白、有点冷色调的粉——和 <a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/18533.html\">Pantone 对于今年流行色预测中的“粉晶”差不多</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161305wQ6oUVAgcTEufjxm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56210526\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p>大面积的粉红里最简单的当属粉色大衣，日常穿着就选粉晶、淡粉（Pale Pink）最保险。不会显皮肤黑，还看起来很柔和沉静，倒是有点像中性色的效果。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061613067aVQesd5UT1nqSGH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.78663239\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">有些人不喜欢太过极简主义的服装，担心那样的款式很容易跑偏到“性冷淡”之列。那就可以尝试一个系列中粉色的那一件，绝对可以把冰冷气质削弱。当然也有人就是爱极简、不爱多余的颜色和设计，粉色也未尝不可，不必担心张扬或者显得廉价。像来自瑞典的品牌 Acne Studios 最近几年凭借简洁和质感大火，他们也挺爱粉色的，最让人记忆深刻的就是其创意总监 Jonny Johansson 让自己 11 岁的儿子担当一件粉色长款大衣的模特。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161306Dtf5yMFq0eNo6Cbi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">搭配同样素净的白色、灰色最合适不过了。一件粉色长款大衣里穿条黑色裤子搭配黑白色的运动鞋、高跟鞋都挺不错的。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161307PjJIcD7Bf1NRXV6l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161308abvqeF6k7Xx3EA8C.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\">当然可以根据自己的肤色选择合适的，不管是更苍白还是更红的粉各有优势。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161308tCFV6uGcZ31jk5sX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161309nXi6rlJjMW8Vz3Ga.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56214689\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">白色大衣在冬天特别亮眼，甚至有点仙气，也是很多人挚爱的颜色。但如果想要稍显低调的话，用毛茸茸的质地、乳白色或者搭配球鞋都显得更活泼一些。看起来银色的夹克配白色内搭和长裤也挺不错。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161309mexFd1Nfr5BWMvSY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68518519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161310kDjUhpRXgZO2S8Qn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75436554\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061613107GXvH5PknWaVDNKp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66538462\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">更大面积还可以从上到下、从内到外的“一身粉”，下图左边是 Christian Wijnants，右边是 Gucci，看起来仍然是越浅、越发白的粉越容易 hold。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161311AspR05EhCeJdnBIM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\" style=\"text-align: left;\">Prada 更浅的粉和 Ralph Lauren 接近裸色的粉看起来就平易近人多了：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161311Y8yq6hQIb34g5Nzn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Prada</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161312S5GoFDu8fsdnalHW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Ralph Lauren</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">可以穿浅粉色的毛衣加裤子，外面套件深色的大衣。或者深浅不一的粉和白色搭在一起，比如白色毛衣加条粉色阔腿裤。 </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161312oykDY78tiPCn0OcU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161313rVkXd4K9i8HgfOGC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.86604775\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">就一条粉色或白色的伞裙也能柔化一身暗色的打扮，增加亮眼元素。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161313SAz6awHnB54iWsjV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Marni 则用偏紫的粉色上衣作内搭，还有玫瑰金色的丝质上衣，显得更成熟优雅。粉嫩的无袖裙里面可以穿高领毛衣，同样都有蝴蝶结，这个颜色却是可爱扮相。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161314HvT6VghD5oaY1cjl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161314PoM0ptsk7EKilZQx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">粉色皮草也可以一试，这样粉嫩的颜色刚好可以降低皮草与生俱来的老气横秋气质。Rihanna 也验证了黑皮肤穿粉色完全没问题。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161315J82dhRtXIBHUCnPz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76643074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">如果还是不习惯穿粉色为主的衣服，粉色的配件可以成为亮点。这个时候不管是浅色还是亮粉的运动鞋穿在大衣底下显得很青春。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161315TAzp3EehFGj8dcNf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7541713\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">粉色的围巾、包袋、帽子……那就太多，不一一介绍了。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161316CTql6UmGsEg1yZkn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161316TlXcZ8eEiG3O457r.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Alexander Wang</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">最后，如果想欣赏粉色如何点缀细节，看 Gucci 早秋系列就够了。这里的粉色的丝带、刺绣花朵、领口大花、各式条纹、包边、帽子和袖口……应有尽有 。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161317cowVAB2UQP4lNbJe.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161317kWfbwXeNqihC59IV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75621891\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160606161319v2yYnkLtxUFQad8w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606061613199842GPQjXDbFmBuJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75185185\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n        \r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}